In HTMLElement children array,

it should not add Whitespace Trim Characters (WTC) if the liquid drop does not
break on a new line
<div>{% if condition %}hello{% endif %}</div>

it should add wtc if the liquid drop breaks on a new line and the previous/next
characters were not spaces.
<div>
  {%- if condition -%}
    aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
  {%- endif -%}
</div>
<div>
  <img>
  {%- if condition %}aaaaaa{% endif -%}
</div>

it should not add wtc if the liquid drop breaks on a new line and the
previous/next characters were spaces
<div>
  {% if condition %}
    aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
  {% endif %}
</div>

